			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2169511">
									

<p>Actually, I chose the name &quot;Roderick Xavier Freeman&quot; because it sounds badass, and because of the freed slaves thing: It makes his ethnicity ambiguous, which allows the reader to make up their own mind on what he looks like. If I wanted &quot; John Everyman,&quot; I'd have named him Smith. As far as the &quot;Freeman in dystopia&quot; thing is concerned, I didn't even consider that.</p>

