			<div class="content" id="post-content-2174523">
									

<p>No problem :)</p>
<p>It's not just the excessive exposition, though; it's that what's happened could stand to be a lot more interesting. ;x In fact, you could've gotten away with this amount of exposition if the content had been a bit more fascinating.</p>
<p>That's hard to do on a mobile device with a short deadline, of course&#8230; but you have the chance to rewrite now, at least! :)</p>

